NAME
       tasklist_applet - Tasklist Applet for the GNOME panel.

SYNOPSIS
       tasklist_applet [ --activate-goad-server [=GOAD_ID]]


DESCRIPTION
       tasklist_applet displays a table showing windowed applica­
       tions running on your computer. Depending on  the  options
       chosen,  you  can display either those on the desktop cur­
       rently in use, or on all virtual desktops.

       To add this applet to a Panel, right-click  on  the  Panel
       and choose Applets->Utility->Tasklist.

OPTIONS
       --activate-goad-server
              (Internal use only) GOAD server ID to activate.

              GOAD_ID     is     usually    the    applet    name
              [tasklist_applet]

